    "theory": "This section lists the various namespaces available in DWSIM's API, organizing its classes, interfaces, and methods into logical groups. The primary global namespace is 'DWSIM', with sub-namespaces covering specific functionalities like AI convergence assistance, automation, drawing, dynamics management, file storage, flowsheet operations, global settings, interfaces, mathematical operations, shared classes, simulation, thermodynamics, UI components, and unit operations.",
