    "topic": "Steady-state simulation creation and configuration",
    "steps": [
      "Click the 'Create a new steady-state simulation' button in the welcome window.",
      "Add or remove compounds and petroleum fractions in the Compounds tab.",
      "Configure Property Packages, flash algorithms, and thermodynamic models in the Basis tab.",
      "Manage Systems of Units in the System of Units tab.",
      "Control flowsheeting environment behaviors in the Behavior tab.",
      "Define object properties for flowsheet floating tables in the Object Properties tab.",
      "Set simulation information such as title, author, and password in the Information tab."
    ],
    "params": {},
